": "SweetBeef", "created": 1778906465863, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Easzq8", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsUQMcam.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/DefiantLs/status/2055504527395279214", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\ud83e\udd23\ud83d\udc49 Wajahat Ali: Pakistani people don\u2019t want to come to the US because of Trump", "last_comment_created": 1778967576255, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 136, "score_up": 866, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 33, "created": 1778905443000, "id": "2055504527395279214", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2055504436743766016/img/0TlB0prrNP4b0lkl.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2055504436743766016/pl/6Bg8DCv-WvREosne.m3u8?v=b51", "aspectRatio": [261, 148], "heightRatio": 56, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2055504436743766016/vid/avc1/476x270/EQCHKgmndEQfD5Ii.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1428167484406964229/Q8fS7M5X_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Defiant L\u2019s", "username": "DefiantLs"}, "content": "Wajahat Ali: Pakistani people don\u2019t want to come to the US because of Trump", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 26}}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83e\udd21\ud83c\udf0e\u00a0\u00a0HONK\u00a0\u00a0HONK\u00a0\u00a0\ud83c\udf0e\ud83e\udd21", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsURVZc1", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 34, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8622389, "raw_content": "Impeachment is the only method for Constitutional removal of a sitting President from Office.  After a President has left office, it is a moot point.\n\nFurthermore, there is no provision for a Senate from a later Congress to try an impeached person by a previous Congress.\n\nThe fact of the matter is Bill Cassidy of LA, made a political judgement that Donald Trump's political shelf life had expired.  He decided to forcefully distance himself from Trump in 2021 after running a campaign where his ads framed him as a virtual wingman for Trump.\n\nHis calculation was wrong.  \n\nCassidy may not even make the runoff.\n\nEdit:  Cassidy has missed the runoff.", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1778969748317, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Voting to Convict a Private Citizen in the Senate is Simply Not a Thing - Cassidy Will Find that Out...", "last_comment_created": 1778969748316, "content": "<p>Impeachment is the only method for Constitutional removal of a sitting President from Office.  After a President has left office, it is a moot point.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, there is no provision for a Senate from a later Congress to try an impeached person by a previous Congress.</p>\n<p>The fact of the matter is Bill Cassidy of LA, made a political judgement that Donald Trump's political shelf life had expired.  He decided to forcefully distance himself from Trump in 2021 after running a campaign where his ads framed him as a virtual wingman for Trump.</p>\n<p>His calculation was wrong.</p>\n<p>Cassidy may not even make the runoff.</p>\n<p>Edit:  Cassidy has missed the runoff.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 34, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2055425136552006124", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsUQOoqt", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 97, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8621907, "raw_content": "", "author": "DylanPatrick", "created": 1778948957131, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "anotherthing", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsUQOoqt.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/marceelias/status/2055425136552006124", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Marc Elias Big Mad about Tina Peters being released. ", "last_comment_created": 1778954626896, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 10, "score_up": 97, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": {"image": "https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/2055395384575270913/YElC4sf0?format=jpg&name=800x419", "domain": "www.democracydocket.com", "description": "Peters was convicted in 2024 after prosecutors showed she facilitated unauthorized access to voting equipment and helped expose sensitive data, actions driven by false claim